Corporal punishment
Where counselling fails other approaches such as corporal punishment should be exacted, given that there are students who cannot reform unless the cane is applied.
 On the other hand, it has been a salutary lesson for parents during the corona break after realising the tough challenge of containing their children at home and imparting discipline to the restless youths.
I am sure by now they have realised and appreciated the fact that teachers go through a lot of difficulties performing the roles of both teachers and parents at the same time.
Responsible citizens
However, parents cannot shirk from their responsibilities and dump children in school for teachers to mould into responsible citizens.
School years are measured and after a certain period, the students will either come back home to live with their parents or join the outside world.
Depending on whether one was disciplined in school or otherwise, the world out there will deal with them accordingly.
Whichever way, parents cannot run away from shouldering the responsibility of ensuring that their children are moulded into role models for future generations.



